text: Ingo Wittenborn (born 30 September 1964) is a German former cyclist. He competed in the individual pursuit event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:German male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of West Germany Category:Cyclists at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
